        "subject": "LU-1575 ptlrpc: client fix for the flock policy combinations",
        "message": "LU-1575 ptlrpc: client fix for the flock policy combinations\n\nThe current patch is intended to fix the issue with incorrect flock\npolicy determining. This issue is observed when 1.8 clients\nwith updated flock policies try to connect to the 2.x servers.\nThis patch is intended for the 1.8 clients to be recognized on the\nupdated 2.x servers.\n\nXyratex-bug-id: MRP-489\n\nReviewed-by: Alexey Lyashkov <alexey_lyashkov@xyratex.com>\nReviewed-by: Andriy Skulysh <andriy_skulysh@xyratex.com>\n\nSigned-off-by: Iurii Golovach <iurii_golovach@xyratex.com>\nChange-Id: Ifc9de713e16e3301e45db8e1cff000ed94205359\n"
      },
